{"tid":2272734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國大選｜史上最年輕政治新丁 25歲共和黨考索恩成首位「90後」眾議員","createTime":"2020-11-05T08:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T08:54:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a86ff5e29a061aad1db83438c4cfd61498e4c07","tid":2272734,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"考索恩是一間房地產投資公司行政總裁，18歲時遇上車禍導致半身癱瘓，但憑藉口才了得，成為激勵人心的演說家。他立場保守，在競選時曾表態支持宗教自由、邊境安全和反對墮胎。<br />\n<br />\n據美國眾議院的紀錄，歷史上最年輕眾議員是田納西州的克萊本（William Charles Cole Claiborne），他在1797年當選眾議員時只有22歲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201105/F77AUFRS4JAR7FBRO3FB23KS2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201105%2FF77AUFRS4JAR7FBRO3FB23KS2Q%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4P3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=42a80eeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201105%2FF77AUFRS4JAR7FBRO3FB23KS2Q%2F&h=c72f2fd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201105/F77AUFRS4JAR7FBRO3FB23KS2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"497257df806a30a6c2e6dee78b7c85ab2d9de93a","tid":2272734,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"乜撚野中文黎 內文講二百年來<br />\n但標題又史上最年輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}